init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The movie was about my life, and I was the main character.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I watched my life unfold in front of my eyes, and it was amazing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was able to see everything that I had done, and I was able to see the thoughts that I had during my life.
